ingredientsDesc:
R1 Imidazole: 58.0 mmol/L, pH 6.0; N-acetylcysteine: 40.0 mmol/L; EDTA:
   3.0 mmol/L; AMP: 10.0 mmol/L; diadenosine pentaphosphate: 24.0 μmol/L;
   NADP+: 9.5 mmol/L; Mg2+: 20.0 mmol/L; D-glucose: 40.0 mmol/L; stabilizer
R2 EDTA: 3.0 mmol/L, pH 9.1; HK (yeast): ≥ 600 μkat/L; G6PDH

   180 mmol/L; N-methyldiethanolamine: 69.0 mmol/L; monoclonal murine
   antibodies inhibiting human CK-M (inhibiting capacity ≥ 2000 U/L of
   CK-MM); preservative; stabilizer; detergent
